ygData.messageBody:
vashi,

you need to go to najena to get the whip, getting it aint easy to do seeing
as how you have to kill a tentacle terror...but its worth it, my warrior now
has two of them...great weapon, the spped is unbelivable, bad thing is the
terrors are about level 20 or so...so get a group if you are near that level
and head off to Najena!
